!!【柯林斯英汉双解大词典】

:<div>

African /ˈæfrɪkən/

(Africans) 

1. ADJ African means belonging or relating to the continent of Africa, or to its countries or people. 非洲的; 非洲国家的 

例： ...the African continent. …非洲大陆。 

例： ...African countries. …非洲国家。 

2. ADJ African means belonging or relating to black people who come from Africa. 属于非洲人的; 与非洲人有关的 

例： ...traditional African culture. …非洲传统文化。 

例： ...dance music with African roots. …源自非洲的舞曲。 

3. ADJ African is used to describe someone, usually a black person, who comes from Africa. 非洲裔的 

例： ...African women. …非洲妇女。 

4. N-COUNT An African is someone who is African. 非洲人 

例： Fish is a staple in the diet of many Africans. 鱼是很多非洲人饮食中的主食。

</div>

